  "texts": [
    "As an example, when I posed this inquiry to ChatGPT \"In the sentence 'Jon wants to be a guitarist because he thinks it is a beautiful instrument.'",
    "what does 'it' refer to?",
    "\", it answered \"the pronoun 'it' refers to 'a beautiful instrument'.\".",
    "When requested to construct a sentence such that the fourth word starts with 'y', ChatGPT failed to produce a valid response.",
    "When queried if the word \"hello\" could be constructed from the letters in the sentence \"hey, can you help me?\""
  ],
